        <description>&lt;img src="https://whylove.top/" alt="Featured image of post 博客的起因经过结果" /&gt;&lt;p&gt;纯粹是闲出屁来了，最开始是因为在b站上看到有推销服务器的，恰巧我当时对这个比较感兴趣。&lt;strong&gt;于是我就在想我是不是也可以整一台云服务器&lt;/strong&gt;，当机立断就找妈妈要了100块钱，然后就在网上选到了阿里云的&lt;strong&gt;2h2g加峰值200m宽带&lt;/strong&gt;，&lt;picture&gt;&lt;source type=&#34;image/avif&#34; srcset=&#34;https://whylove.top/generated/image-variants/9b21c52949b4/635230854062/responsive_content-320.avif 320w, https://whylove.top/generated/image-variants/9b21c52949b4/635230854062/responsive_content-480.avif 480w, https://whylove.top/generated/image-variants/9b21c52949b4/635230854062/responsive_content-960.avif 960w&#34; sizes=&#34;(min-width: 1024px) 864px, (min-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 64px), calc(100vw - 32px)&#34;&gt;&lt;source type=&#34;image/webp&#34; srcset=&#34;https://whylove.top/generated/image-variants/9b21c52949b4/635230854062/responsive_content-320.webp 320w, https://whylove.top/generated/image-variants/9b21c52949b4/635230854062/responsive_content-480.webp 480w, https://whylove.top/generated/image-variants/9b21c52949b4/635230854062/responsive_content-960.webp 960w&#34; sizes=&#34;(min-width: 1024px) 864px, (min-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 64px), calc(100vw - 32px)&#34;&gt;&lt;img
